wpt.desc: Son Of Safe Resource by cyberspnr, Traditional Cache (1.5/1)

groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: Son Of Safe Resource
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: This is a quick cache and dash that is easily accessible.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
Put away your GPS; you won't get much of a reading when you are at GZ. Re-read the title and use your geosense. This is a nano cache, so you will have to bring your own pen.
This cache is very near the former location of "Safe Resource".
Congratulations to iablublurr for FTF!
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:encoded_hints: Think inside the box and let your fingers do the walking.

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Required patience because of muggle traffic, but I got it.
